description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 53, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 159, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
